					<div id="contentSub"><div id="mw-content-subtitle"></div></div>
					
					
					<div id="mw-content-text" class="mw-body-content"><div class="mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output" lang="en" dir="ltr"><div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">Flag of a country or nation</div>
<p class="mw-empty-elt">
</p>
<figure class="mw-default-size" typeof="mw:File/Thumb"><a href="/wiki/File:Flickr_-_%E2%80%A6trialsanderrors_-_Johnson%27s_new_chart_of_national_emblems,_1868.jpg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d8/Flickr_-_%E2%80%A6trialsanderrors_-_Johnson%27s_new_chart_of_national_emblems%2C_1868.jpg/370px-Flickr_-_%E2%80%A6trialsanderrors_-_Johnson%27s_new_chart_of_national_emblems%2C_1868.jpg" decoding="async" width="370" height="271" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d8/Flickr_-_%E2%80%A6trialsanderrors_-_Johnson%27s_new_chart_of_national_emblems%2C_1868.jpg/555px-Flickr_-_%E2%80%A6trialsanderrors_-_Johnson%27s_new_chart_of_national_emblems%2C_1868.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d8/Flickr_-_%E2%80%A6trialsanderrors_-_Johnson%27s_new_chart_of_national_emblems%2C_1868.jpg/740px-Flickr_-_%E2%80%A6trialsanderrors_-_Johnson%27s_new_chart_of_national_emblems%2C_1868.jpg 2x" data-file-width="8187" data-file-height="5991" /></a><figcaption><i>Johnson's new chart of national emblems</i>, published <abbr title="circa">c.</abbr><span style="white-space:nowrap;">&#8201;1868</span>. The large flags shown in the corners are the <a href="/wiki/Flag_of_the_United_States#Historical_progression_of_designs" title="Flag of the United States">37-star flag of the United States</a> (flown 1867–1890), upper left; the <a href="/wiki/Royal_Standard_of_the_United_Kingdom" title="Royal Standard of the United Kingdom">Royal Standard of the United Kingdom</a>, upper, right; the <a href="/wiki/Russian_Imperial_Standard" class="mw-redirect" title="Russian Imperial Standard">Russian Imperial Standard</a>, lower left; and the <a href="/wiki/Flag_of_France" title="Flag of France">French tricolore</a> with inset <a href="/wiki/French_Imperial_Eagle" title="French Imperial Eagle">Imperial Eagle</a>, lower right. Various other flags flown by ships are shown. The <a href="/wiki/Flag_of_Cuba" title="Flag of Cuba">Flag of Cuba</a> is labelled "Cuban <a href="/wiki/Ten_Years%27_War" title="Ten Years&#39; War">(so called)</a>". The <a href="/wiki/Chinese_dragon" title="Chinese dragon">Chinese dragon</a> on the <a href="/wiki/Flag_of_the_Qing_Dynasty" class="mw-redirect" title="Flag of the Qing Dynasty">Flag of China</a> was drawn mistakenly as a western <a href="/wiki/Dragon" title="Dragon">dragon</a>.</figcaption></figure>
